# game/Scenes/CounselorChats/Conversations/1 - Missing Father.rpy:7
translate german counselorconversation1_16a1cf46:

    # pc "We still haven't found anything about my dad."
    pc "Wir haben immer noch nichts über meinen Vater herausgefunden."

# game/Scenes/CounselorChats/Conversations/1 - Missing Father.rpy:8
translate german counselorconversation1_054aff41:

    # sc "Really? The police can't tell you anything."
    sc "Wirklich? Die Polizei kann dir nichts sagen?"

# game/Scenes/CounselorChats/Conversations/1 - Missing Father.rpy:9
translate german counselorconversation1_c683266e:

    # pc "No. They've actually been pretty useless."
    pc "Nein. Die waren eigentlich ziemlich nutzlos."

# game/Scenes/CounselorChats/Conversations/1 - Missing Father.rpy:10
translate german counselorconversation1_4c1a5168:

    # sc "That must be very frustrating for you and your family."
    sc "Das muss für dich und deine Familie sehr frustrierend sein."

# game/Scenes/CounselorChats/Conversations/1 - Missing Father.rpy:11
translate german counselorconversation1_07157d28:

    # pc "It is."
    pc "Das ist es."

# game/Scenes/CounselorChats/Conversations/1 - Missing Father.rpy:12
translate german counselorconversation1_18fdb724:

    # pc "The lead detective seems to care, but she doesn't have enough people to help her."
    pc "Die leitende Ermittlerin scheint sich darum zu kümmern, aber sie hat nicht genug Leute, die ihr helfen."

# game/Scenes/CounselorChats/Conversations/1 - Missing Father.rpy:13
translate german counselorconversation1_8369ad8b:

    # pc "She actually even asked me to investigate on my own some."
    pc "Sie hat mich sogar gebeten, selbst ein bisschen zu recherchieren."

# game/Scenes/CounselorChats/Conversations/1 - Missing Father.rpy:14
translate german counselorconversation1_a9eb7aa9:

    # sc "But you haven't found anything?"
    sc "Aber du hast nichts gefunden?"

# game/Scenes/CounselorChats/Conversations/1 - Missing Father.rpy:16
translate german counselorconversation1_d02147ef:

    # pc "I've found some things that seem like they may lead somewhere, but nothing solid yet."
    pc "Ich habe ein paar Dinge gefunden, die vielleicht irgendwohin führen könnten, aber noch nichts Konkretes."

# game/Scenes/CounselorChats/Conversations/1 - Missing Father.rpy:17
translate german counselorconversation1_5b9f9e80:

    # pc "The more I find, the more worried about him I get."
    pc "Je mehr ich finde, desto mehr mache ich mir Sorgen um ihn."

# game/Scenes/CounselorChats/Conversations/1 - Missing Father.rpy:19
translate german counselorconversation1_cd5c81b7:

    # pc "There's probably some things of his I could look through in the basement, but I haven't had a chance to do that yet."
    pc "Im Keller gibt es wahrscheinlich ein paar Sachen von ihm, die ich durchsehen könnte, aber dazu hatte ich noch keine Gelegenheit."

# game/Scenes/CounselorChats/Conversations/1 - Missing Father.rpy:20
translate german counselorconversation1_cef820fb:

    # sc "Did you have a good relationship with your father?"
    sc "Hattest du ein gutes Verhältnis zu deinem Vater?"

# game/Scenes/CounselorChats/Conversations/1 - Missing Father.rpy:21
translate german counselorconversation1_f29c1b7f:

    # pc "I used to. My mom died when I was young. Cancer."
    pc "Früher schon. Meine Mutter ist gestorben, als ich noch klein war. An Krebs."

# game/Scenes/CounselorChats/Conversations/1 - Missing Father.rpy:22
translate german counselorconversation1_bd0faada:

    # sc "I'm so sorry."
    sc "Das tut mir so leid."

# game/Scenes/CounselorChats/Conversations/1 - Missing Father.rpy:23
translate german counselorconversation1_0b983a40:

    # pc "It's okay. My dad and I were practically inseparable when I was growing up though."
    pc "Ist schon okay. Mein Vater und ich waren aber praktisch unzertrennlich, als ich aufwuchs."

# game/Scenes/CounselorChats/Conversations/1 - Missing Father.rpy:24
translate german counselorconversation1_a44baf9d:

    # pc "During the last few years, we'd sort of lost contact."
    pc "In den letzten Jahren hatten wir den Kontakt irgendwie verloren."

# game/Scenes/CounselorChats/Conversations/1 - Missing Father.rpy:25
translate german counselorconversation1_5b951843:

    # pc "My fault. I should have done better."
    pc "Meine Schuld. Ich hätte mich mehr anstrengen sollen."

# game/Scenes/CounselorChats/Conversations/1 - Missing Father.rpy:26
translate german counselorconversation1_2d7b47cc:

    # pc "I was upset about Lisa. He just brought her into our life without even asking me."
    pc "Ich war sauer wegen Lisa. Er hat sie einfach in unser Leben gebracht, ohne mich überhaupt zu fragen."

# game/Scenes/CounselorChats/Conversations/1 - Missing Father.rpy:27
translate german counselorconversation1_c66f26fb:

    # pc "It felt like he was trying to replace Mom."
    pc "Es kam mir so vor, als wollte er Mama ersetzen."

# game/Scenes/CounselorChats/Conversations/1 - Missing Father.rpy:30
translate german counselorconversation1_b5c403cc:

    # pc "But I see now that I was an idiot. Lisa is great and Dad deserved to be happy."
    pc "Aber jetzt sehe ich ein, dass ich ein Idiot war. Lisa ist toll und Papa hat es verdient, glücklich zu sein."

# game/Scenes/CounselorChats/Conversations/1 - Missing Father.rpy:31
translate german counselorconversation1_8836c69a:

    # pc "I said all these horrible things and now I feel like I might never get to apologize for them."
    pc "Ich habe all diese schrecklichen Dinge gesagt und jetzt habe ich das Gefühl, dass ich mich vielleicht nie dafür entschuldigen kann."

# game/Scenes/CounselorChats/Conversations/1 - Missing Father.rpy:32
translate german counselorconversation1_18626ff2:

    # sc "I'm sure he knows."
    sc "Ich bin sicher, er weiß es."

# game/Scenes/CounselorChats/Conversations/1 - Missing Father.rpy:33
translate german counselorconversation1_fef3613e:

    # sc "We all say horrible things that we don't mean at times."
    sc "Wir alle sagen manchmal schreckliche Dinge, die wir nicht so meinen."

# game/Scenes/CounselorChats/Conversations/1 - Missing Father.rpy:34
translate german counselorconversation1_a11cad70:

    # sc "It seems like your father really loves you. He knows you didn't mean the things you said."
    sc "Es scheint, als würde dein Vater dich wirklich lieben. Er weiß, dass du die Dinge, die du gesagt hast, nicht so gemeint hast."

# game/Scenes/CounselorChats/Conversations/1 - Missing Father.rpy:35
translate german counselorconversation1_ca81368e:

    # sc "You have to keep your hopes up that you'll get to tell him yourself soon."
    sc "Du musst die Hoffnung nicht aufgeben, dass du es ihm bald selbst sagen kannst."

# game/Scenes/CounselorChats/Conversations/1 - Missing Father.rpy:36
translate german counselorconversation1_4898a76c:

    # sc "If the police are asking you to help with their investigation, they probably don't suspect foul play."
    sc "Wenn die Polizei dich bittet, bei ihren Ermittlungen zu helfen, vermuten sie wahrscheinlich kein Verbrechen."

# game/Scenes/CounselorChats/Conversations/1 - Missing Father.rpy:37
translate german counselorconversation1_b102cc1c:

    # sc "Which means your father is likely still out there somewhere and you'll get to talk to him and tell him how you feel."
    sc "Das bedeutet, dass dein Vater wahrscheinlich noch irgendwo da draußen ist und du mit ihm sprechen und ihm sagen kannst, wie du dich fühlst."

# game/Scenes/CounselorChats/Conversations/1 - Missing Father.rpy:38
translate german counselorconversation1_d2e265a2:

    # sc "Keep your chin up and keep looking for him."
    sc "Lass den Kopf nicht hängen und such weiter nach ihm."

# game/Scenes/CounselorChats/Conversations/1 - Missing Father.rpy:40
translate german counselorconversation1_c59127f2:

    # "I wipe my eyes, a little embarrassed that I had cried in front of her."
    "Ich wische mir die Augen ab, ein wenig verlegen, dass ich vor ihr geweint habe."

# game/Scenes/CounselorChats/Conversations/1 - Missing Father.rpy:41
translate german counselorconversation1_9b73ec6c:

    # "I haven't ever really sat down with somebody and poured out my thoughts about my dad."
    "Ich habe mich noch nie wirklich mit jemandem hingesetzt und meine Gedanken über meinen Vater ausgeschüttet."

# game/Scenes/CounselorChats/Conversations/1 - Missing Father.rpy:42
translate german counselorconversation1_0d136ca5:

    # "It feels good to get it off my chest."
    "Es tut gut, mir das von der Seele zu reden."

# game/Scenes/CounselorChats/Conversations/1 - Missing Father.rpy:43
translate german counselorconversation1_848a845c:

    # pc "Thanks, Mrs. Spann."
    pc "Danke, Mrs. Spann."

# game/Scenes/CounselorChats/Conversations/1 - Missing Father.rpy:45
translate german counselorconversation1_b2c078dc:

    # sc "Please, call me Gertrude."
    sc "Bitte, nenn mich Gertrude."

# game/Scenes/CounselorChats/Conversations/1 - Missing Father.rpy:46
translate german counselorconversation1_d778ea2f:

    # pc "Thank you Gertrude."
    pc "Danke, Gertrude."

# game/Scenes/CounselorChats/Conversations/1 - Missing Father.rpy:47
translate german counselorconversation1_ee261a5c:

    # sc "Well, we're about out of time. You better get to class."
    sc "Nun, unsere Zeit ist fast um. Du solltest besser zum Unterricht gehen."

# game/Scenes/CounselorChats/Conversations/1 - Missing Father.rpy:48
translate german counselorconversation1_1886e845:

    # sc "I'm so glad you came in and talked to me though. Feel free to come in any time in the morning before class."
    sc "Ich bin aber so froh, dass du hereingekommen bist und mit mir gesprochen hast. Komm gerne jederzeit morgens vor dem Unterricht vorbei."

# game/Scenes/CounselorChats/Conversations/1 - Missing Father.rpy:49
translate german counselorconversation1_fa6f2867:

    # pc "I'm sure I will. This was good for me."
    pc "Das werde ich sicher. Das hat mir gutgetan."

# game/Scenes/CounselorChats/Conversations/1 - Missing Father.rpy:50
translate german counselorconversation1_56b6e989:

    # sc "I'm glad."
    sc "Das freut mich."

# game/Scenes/CounselorChats/Conversations/1 - Missing Father.rpy:51
translate german counselorconversation1_e4b88e88:

    # "With that, I stand up and head to class."
    "Damit stehe ich auf und gehe zum Unterricht."

